          <h3 class="text-center" id="pg1"> Guest Book</h3>
          <br>
          <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
            <h4>Description</h4>
            <p>
              The MAZI Guest Book is an open source application that can used in events enabling the audience to share their thoughts, photos, etc
            </p>
            <img src="images/guestbook_doc.png" class="img-responsive center-block" alt="Image for NextCloud Admin Panel" style='padding-bottom: 10px'>
            <h4>Administration Guide</h4>
            <p>
              To moderate the content, you go to <b>http://local.mazizone.eu:8081/#admin</b> (username: <b>admin</b> password: <b>mazizone</b>), where you can delete submission that are inappropriate
            </p>
            <p>
               For slideshow <b>http://local.mazizone.eu:8081/projection</b>
            </p>
              <h4>Useful Guidelines</h4>
               <p>You can modify the appearance of the GuestBook</p>
             <ul>
                <li>Tags</li>
                <li>Background Image</li>
                <li>Admin Password</li>
                <li>Message</li>
             </ul>               
              <p>
                First logging into your Raspberry pi. The login for raspberry is</br> 
                 <b>User Name:</b> pi</br>
                 <b>Password:</b> mazizone
                </p>
                 <b>Tags</b>
                 <p> 
                  In order to change tags,Open the config.js file, which takes place in this path: /var/www/html/mazi-board/src/www/js/config.js</br> 
                  You can remove or edit a tag as you wish in this code line</br>  
                  <pre><code>
                    tags: ['Artist', 'Activist', 'Male', 'Female', 'Student', 'Professor', 'DSIMaker', 'PolicyMaker']
                  </code></pre>
                </p>
                 <b>Backgournd Image</b>
                 <p>
                  In order to change the backgournd image,save the image you want in this following path:/var/www/html/mazi-board/src/www/images</br>
                  Replace the DSI.jpg of the following code, with the name of your image.</br>
                  This code path is placed to /var/www/html/mazi-board/src/www/js/templates/header_tmpl.html </br>  
                  <pre>
                    <code>
                      &lt;div class="header-bar"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                      &lt;div class="header-image column"&gt;&lt;img src="images/DSI.jpg"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
                    </code>
                  </pre>
                </p>
                 <b>Admin Password</b> 
                 <p>
                  In order to change the admin password, open the config.js file ,which takes place in this path: /var/www/html/mazi-board/src/node/config.js,</br>
                  and then fill  the <b>authPassword</b> with the password you like. 
                  <pre>
                    <code>
                      /* AUTH DATA */
                        authName: 'admin',
                        authPassword: 'password',
                    </code>
                  </pre>
                 </p>
                 <b>Message</b>
                 <p>
                  In order to change the message, open the submission_input_tmpl.html file , which takes place in this path:/var/www/html/mazi-board/src/www/js/templates/submission_input_tmpl.html,</br> 
                  and then change the message <b>(Click here to join the Guest Book...)</b> With the message you wish to be displayed  
                 </p>
              </p>
